text: Yelkan Tedeyev (29 December 1938 - 3 October 1984) was a Soviet wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle 63 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:1984 deaths Category:Soviet male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of the Soviet Union Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics
